Troubleshooting
Connection Errors: Ensure MongoDB is running and accessible at the URL specified in your .env file.
Duplicate Key Errors: Ensure that the email and username fields are unique across your database.
Environment Variables: Double-check that your .env file is correctly configured and loaded.
